comments.body:
@lcarva Oh, wow. I didn’t realize the extent of the issue.

Sadly we can’t reasonably change the behavior of the existing command.

@jaikiran it might be warranted to add a single-letter option to disable the tag listing, though (`-t`?`-n`? `-l`?) Absolutely non-blocking, it can be added any time later.

@jaikiran I’m sorry for the delay.

I’m afraid I’m mostly not available for the following week.

Could @vrothberg , @rhatdan and others come to a consensus in the meantime? If not, I’m tempted to merge as is, after I return.
